<p><compono-error-inline><span slot="title">Invalid parameter usage</span><span slot="description">Parameters cannot be used in the root context.</span></compono-error-inline><br><compono-error-inline><span slot="title">Parameter component call in root content</span><span slot="description">The parameter component call <strong>comp</strong> cannot be used outside of a component definition.</span></compono-error-inline></p>
